"title": "8205: childlikeness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8205: childlikeness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An attitude of simple trust and faith, to be distinguished from childishness. It is commended by Scripture as an appropriate attitude for the believer to take towards God.</p>\n<h2>God treats his people like children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:12\">NUM 11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:15\">ISA 49:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:13\">ISA 66:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:20\">JER 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:17\">ROM 8:14–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:1-Gal4:7\">GAL 4:1–4:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's people should respond to God as children to a parent</h2>\n<h3>In trust</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps131:2\">PSA 131:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14\">1PE 1:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In humility</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:46-Luke9:48\">LUK 9:46–9:48</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:2-Matt18:5\">MAT 18:2–18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:33-Mark9:37\">MRK 9:33–9:37</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:7\">1KI 3:7</a> <em>Solomon</em></p>\n<h3>In innocence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:15\">MRK 10:13–10:15</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:14\">MAT 19:13–19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a></p>\n<h3>In imitating a model</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1JN 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Childlikeness is reflected in pastoral care</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:7\">1TH 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:28\">1JN 2:28</a></p>\n<h2>Childlikeness is to be distinguished from immature childishness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:1-1Cor3:3\">1CO 3:1–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:12-Heb6:1\">HEB 5:12–6:1</a></p>",
